<gpx xmlns="http://www.topografix.com/GPX/1/1" xmlns:gpxx="http://www.garmin.com/xmlschemas/GpxExtensions/v3" creator="CALTOPO" version="1.1"><metadata><name><![CDATA[Rio en Medio Loop]]></name></metadata><trk><name>Rio en Medio Loop</name><desc>Popularity: 2/5
Difficulty: 3/5
Dates: 5/15 - 11/15

This delicious loop starts at the Norski Trailhead just before you descend to the Ski Resort. This run has a bit of everything: solitude, technical descents down the Winsor to start, smooth flowing downhill forest road running, moderate forest road climbs, and then a steep and rewarding ascent along the gorgeous Rio en Medio before a short, but exhausting return along the Winsor. Take in the sights and sounds of the beautiful riparian areas and meadows along Rio en Medio. One of my favorites.</desc><trkseg><trkpt lat="35.78896663425967" lon="-105.80862582550049"><ele>3137.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78895062183067" lon="-105.80864300773499"><ele>3137.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78896" lon="-105.80899"><ele>3137.5392097514123</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78887" lon="-105.80912000000001"><ele>3135.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.7888" lon="-105.80903"><ele>3132.5445798917117</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78867" lon="-105.80914000000001"><ele>3128.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78845" lon="-105.80921999999998"><ele>3123.107061955856</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78842" lon="-105.80916000000002"><ele>3124.125859830316</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78819" lon="-105.80923999999999"><ele>3120.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78774" lon="-105.80926999999997"><ele>3113.513741626657</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78754" lon="-105.80920000000003"><ele>3109.380035554059</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.7873" lon="-105.80937"><ele>3106.28688919032</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78697" lon="-105.80948999999998"><ele>3101.8650560001843</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78678" lon="-105.80962"><ele>3096.806616889313</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.7866" lon="-105.80966999999998"><ele>3094.4552358929163</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78604" lon="-105.80973"><ele>3081.5330802873286</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78571" lon="-105.80980999999997"><ele>3076.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78552" lon="-105.80974000000003"><ele>3073.929301959177</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.78548" lon="-105.80977999999999"><ele>3072.0</ele></t